## Features

Employee Management

Add new employee

View employee list

Delete employee

Unique employee ID validation

Attendance Management

Mark Present / Absent

View attendance by employee ID

One attendance record per employee per day

Real-time refresh after marking attendance

## System Features

RESTful API using FastAPI

CORS-enabled backend for frontend communication

Fully deployed cloud application

Clean UI with React

## API Endpoints

### Employees

GET /employees â†’ List employees

POST /employees â†’ Add employee

DELETE /employees/{employee_id} â†’ Delete employee

### Attendance

POST /attendance â†’ Mark attendance

GET /attendance/{employee_id} â†’ View attendance

## Local Setup Instructions

1. Clone Repository

git clone

https://github.com/ATUL-SHARMA1215/HRMS.git
cd HRMS

2. Backend Setup

cd backend
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate   # Windows

pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --reload

3. Frontend Setup

cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev

## Deployment 

